Class SubtaskParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • SubtaskParser

  • public class SubtaskParser
extends java.lang.Object
    A class to find subjective expressions in a Salsa XML file specified by the SubjectiveExpressionLocationPath. The found SEs are saved in a HashMap and made accessible for the PresetSELocationModule.
    Author:
    isha, mwolf
